license: "LicenseRef-ConsciousAI-DualLicense"
abstract: >
  ConsciousAI computes a spectral approximation of integrated information (Φ)
  for continuous multivariate time-series systems, enabling real-time monitoring
  of autonomous systems, biomedical devices, financial markets, and LLMs.
  Reduces O(2^N) exact IIT complexity to O(N² log N), achieving sub-millisecond
  computation for N=200 components — a 20x scalability advance over PyPhi.
